version_description:
Improvements, improvements and improvements again!

* Numerous issues regarding Facebook Connect and Server Issues;
* All players will have their connection reward after updating;
* All the small things ;-)

Headquarters, Leader-board and Group challenge are still in development and coming soon! Stay tuned and have fun!

v 0.8.2
Improvements, improvements and improvements again!

And...

Again!

* Greatly improved loading time and added helpful hints to entertain out beloved players! If you have neat idea about loading Hint - send it to us, and we'll add it to the game;
* Quest Rewards increased;
* Numerous improvements regarding Facebook Connect and Server;
* All the small things ;-)

Headquarters, Leader-board and Group challenge are still in development and coming soon! Stay tuned and have fun!

v 0.9.2
Hey, hey, hey! 
Great news everyone!

* Increase your Rank by completing list of special achievements;
* Earn Platinum and upgrade all your equipment to increase coins flow;
* A little bit re-balancing here and there, to make this game even more enjoyable;
* Lots of interface and user experience improvements;
* Billion of small fixes and enhancements;

And we have added a Juice bar over the street. Grand opening soon ;-)
Stay tuned!

v 0.9.4
Greetings!
Small update today:

* Fixed Achievement window layout on some devices;
* Improved game loading process with unstable connection;
* As usual, few small improvements and invisible fixes;

Have a good day everyone!

Another small but important update:

- Improved Loading process even further;

Have a good holidays!

Great news! 
Juice Bar Grand Opening!

• You can open your own Juice Bar to treat your clients with a fresh juices;
• Buy fruit trees, collect fruits and make healthy drinks for your clients;
• Improved character movements on the streets;
• Added Gym visitors queue;
• Fixed crash on loading;
• Improved stability on older devices;

Juice bar improvements on their way in the next update!
Stay tuned!

New version of My Gym! Here's what's new:

• Video Ads are back! Sorry for inconvenience;
• Juice Bar user experience improvements;
• Stability improvements;
• Lot's of improvements in visual effects and player's interface;

Stay in shape! More fun is coming soon!

Dear Players!
We continue our work on this project non-stop.
Here is another small update with various fixes and improvements;

• Daily Bonus reworked. Now you can see what reward you will get;
• Added Achievements to Game Center;
• Added Prestige Points Leader Board with syncing to  Game Center;

Please stay tuned, we're working on great features at the moment!
Tatem Games Team

Dear Players
We've made some improvements and fixed a lot of issues to make this game more fun and enjoyable.
But even more features are in development at the moment and will be added to the game in the nearest future.

Meanwhile My Gym now supports additional languages:
• French;
• German;
• Spanish;
• Italian;
• Portuguese;
• Simplified Chinese;

You can change language in the game setting.
More languages will be added in the future updates.

Enjoy your play and have a good time :-)

Dear Trainers

Happy clients are the most important, so we've made this update!
• Fixed nasty issue with stuck clients;
• Juice Bar tutorial improved;
• Other smaller bug fixes, polishing and improvements;

Please update the game to the latest version.

Great News!

You can hire new staff members to help you manage all Your Clients! 
Trainers will keep train Clients even when you sleep. Get experience points to increase levels of Trainers, which will boost your Coins rewards.

Also, in this update:

• Three new languages supported: Turkish, Japanese, Korean;
• Workstation breakage re-balanced. Your equipment will break less often from now on.
• Fixed achievement Claim button. It will be much easier to claim your rewards.
• Fixed achievement related to harvesting Fruits.
• Re-balanced cost of equipment and expand;
• Reward for Daily Activities increased;
• Other small improvements and bug fixes;


Stay Tuned!

Dear Players
We've made some improvements and fixed a lot of issues to make this game more fun and enjoyable.

• Wheel Of Fortune added;
• Balance of Juice making improved;
• City area changed, sea shore and beach added;
• You can kick unwanted visitors of the Juice Bar;
• Improved game stability;

Stay Tuned!

Hello Dear Players!

Here what's in this fix:
• Wheel Of Fortune now should spin as intended;
• Fixed issue with empty Reward Backpack and Daily Bonus;
• Fixed issue with not receiving resource in case of full storage;
• Improved performance in some troublesome cases;
• Added localization to all of the missing phrases;
• Added purchase warning when connection to the network is poor;
• Fixed issue with a locked beach in Friend's room;

We continue to improve My Gym, and a lot of issues are still under development. But we'll bring new updates to you very soon!
Stay Tuned!

Small update:

• Removed Christmas theme;
• Bug fixes, polishing and improvements;

Dear Players,

In this update:
- fixed bug when some equipment not being sold;
- fixed rare issue when you always get bricks spinning Wheel of Fortune; 
- updated costs for some equipment

Stay Tuned!
